    "content": "There are three sequential commands implemented in this demonstration. | setopt &lt; hostname &gt; &lt; port &gt; &lt; message &gt; - This command specifies the following parameters for the UDP packet: Destination IP Address or Host name, Destination Port and Message to transfer . | getopt - This command displays the current options . | sendudp - This command sends a UDP packet . | . ",
